# Assets Directory

This directory will contain all static assets for the IntelDrop landing page:

## Required Assets

### App Store Assets
- `app-store-badge.svg` - Standard App Store download badge
- `app-store-badge-white.svg` - White version for dark backgrounds

### Branding
- `logo.svg` - Main IntelDrop logo
- `logo-white.svg` - White version for dark backgrounds
- `favicon.ico` - Browser favicon
- `og-image.jpg` - Open Graph image for social sharing

### App Screenshots
- `hero-mockup.png` - Main hero section mockup
- `screenshot-1.png` - Learning Dashboard
- `screenshot-2.png` - Micro Learning interface
- `screenshot-3.png` - Progress Tracking

### Testimonials
- `avatar-1.jpg` - User avatar (Sarah Johnson)
- `avatar-2.jpg` - User avatar (Mike Chen)
- `avatar-3.jpg` - User avatar (Emily Rodriguez)

## Image Optimization Guidelines

- Use modern formats (WebP with fallbacks)
- Optimize for mobile-first loading
- Maintain high quality for Retina displays
- Keep file sizes under 500KB each
- Use appropriate dimensions for responsive design

## Naming Convention

Use descriptive, lowercase names with hyphens:
- `app-store-badge.svg`
- `hero-mockup.png`
- `screenshot-dashboard.png`

This keeps the assets organized and easy to reference in the HTML.